      • driveEncoders

        public void driveEncoders(int encoderDistance,
                          double power)
        Dives using encoders.
        Parameters:
        encoderDistance - Encoder distance to travel.
        power - Double from (-1)-(1) of intensity of the movement positive for forward and negative for reverse.
        Throws:
        InvalidMoveCommandException - Throws this error if the encoders to travel is nonzero and the power is 0.
        DumpsterFireException - Throws this exception if the encoder count is negative.
